<section class="container">
    <div class="match-header">
        <span class="category">
            <%= event.category_name %>
        </span>
        <h1>
            <%= h1 %>
        </h1>
        <p>Watch <%= event.name %> free live stream online. Footybite coverage of <%= event.category_name %>.</p>
        <% if (event.poster) { %>
            <img src="<%= event.poster %>" alt="<%= event.name %>"
                style="width: 100%; max-width: 800px; border-radius: 12px; margin-top: 20px;">
            <% } %>
    </div>

    <div class="player-container">
        <iframe src="<%= event.iframe %>" allowfullscreen scrolling="no"></iframe>
    </div>

    <div class="seo-content">
        <h2>How to Watch <%= event.name %> Live Online</h2>
        <p>Looking for a reliable way to watch <%= event.name %>? You've come to the right place. Footybite (Fotybyte)
                offers free live streaming for this <%= event.category_name %> event. Our streams are optimized for all
                    devices, including mobile, tablet, and desktop.</p>
        <p>To start watching, simply click the play button on the player above. If the stream doesn't load immediately,
            try refreshing the page or checking back closer to the start time: <%= event.time %>.</p>

        <h3>Event Details</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Event:</strong>
                <%= event.name %>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Category:</strong>
                <%= event.category_name %>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Start Time:</strong>
                <%= event.time %>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Platform:</strong> Footybite / Footybyte</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Is <%= event.name %> free to watch?</h4>
            <p>Yes, you can watch <%= event.name %> live stream for free on Footybite. We do not require any
                    subscription or payment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>Where can I find soccer streams for today?</h4>
            <p>You can find all today's soccer streams and other sports events on our homepage or the dedicated category
                pages.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>